column5: Historic craftsman style house on the East Side. Newly remodeled with TWO rooms each with high end queen bed; private bath for guests. Walkable to east side and downtown activities. Enjoy comfortable home with porch swing, grill, fully equipped kitchen, laundry, central AC, his & hers bikes for you to borrow. This is my home and you are renting rooms, not the whole place, but you can have as much privacy as you want! Consider me the groundskeeper of this old home.
